snippet.title: Sonic Moon BETA stuff {30/04/2022} [W.I.P Demo 4]
snippet.description:
I've decided to start working my way up to releasing a 4th demo for either May or June. It will feature the first five zones and more available Sailor Senshi helpers (Moon, Mercury, Mars, Venus and Uranus at the very least).
* Sailor Venus and Uranus gameplay.
* Recomposed a bit of Ruby Ruins Z's music.
* New Super Stages.
* Some added sections to multiple stages.
* Spruced-up RRZ boss.
* Scoreboard.
* Attract mode demo.
* Endless minigame.

Game Jolt Page: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonicthehe...

Sonic is owned by SEGA / Sonic Team.
Sailor Moon is owned by Naoko Takeuchi / Toei.
This project is fan-made and non-profit.

Mario Obsessed - MMXXII
